<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='377000' id='t-377000'>but we don't have a clue how to measure them.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='380000' id='t-380000'>So here's another Einstein quote:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='382000' id='t-382000'>&quot;Not everything that can be counted counts,</span>
