<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='389000' id='t-389000'>I hate to argue with Einstein,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='391000' id='t-391000'>but if that which is most valuable</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='394000' id='t-394000'>in our life and our business</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='396000' id='t-396000'>actually can't be counted or valued,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='399000' id='t-399000'>aren't we going to spend our lives</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='401000' id='t-401000'>just mired in measuring the mundane?</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:55
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='404000' id='t-404000'>It was that sort of heady question about what counts</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='407000' id='t-407000'>that led me to take my CEO hat off for a week</span>
