<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='413000' id='t-413000'>I flew off to a place that's been shrouded in mystery for centuries,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='416000' id='t-416000'>a place some folks call Shangri-La.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='419000' id='t-419000'>It's actually moved from the survival base of the pyramid</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='422000' id='t-422000'>to becoming a transformational</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='424000' id='t-424000'>role model for the world.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='426000' id='t-426000'>I went to Bhutan.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='428000' id='t-428000'>The teenage king of Bhutan was also a curious man,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='430000' id='t-430000'>but this was back in 1972,</span>
