<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='442000' id='t-442000'>On a trip through India,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='444000' id='t-444000'>early in his reign as king,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='447000' id='t-447000'>he was asked by an Indian journalist</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='449000' id='t-449000'>about the Bhutanese GDP,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='451000' id='t-451000'>the size of the Bhutanese GDP.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='454000' id='t-454000'>The king responded in a fashion</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='456000' id='t-456000'>that actually has transformed us four decades later.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='459000' id='t-459000'>He said the following, he said: &quot;Why are we so obsessed</span>
