<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='468000' id='t-468000'>Now, in essence, the king was asking us to consider</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='471000' id='t-471000'>an alternative definition of success,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='473000' id='t-473000'>what has come to be known as</span>
