 8:42
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='511000' id='t-511000'>For the next three dozen years as king,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='514000' id='t-514000'>this king actually started measuring</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='517000' id='t-517000'>and managing around happiness in Bhutan --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='520000' id='t-520000'>including, just recently, taking his country</span>
