</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:03
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='532000' id='t-532000'>So as I spent time with leaders in the GNH movement,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='535000' id='t-535000'>I got to really understand what they're doing.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='537000' id='t-537000'>And I got to spend some time with the prime minister.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='539000' id='t-539000'>Over dinner, I asked him an impertinent question.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='543000' id='t-543000'>I asked him,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='545000' id='t-545000'>&quot;How can you create and measure</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='548000' id='t-548000'>something which evaporates --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='550000' id='t-550000'>in other words, happiness?&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='552000' id='t-552000'>And he's a very wise man, and he said,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='554000' id='t-554000'>&quot;Listen, Bhutan's goal is not to create happiness.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='557000' id='t-557000'>We create the conditions for happiness to occur.</span>
