<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='664000' id='t-664000'>The reality is, in Western countries,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='667000' id='t-667000'>quite often we do focus on the pursuit of happiness</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='670000' id='t-670000'>as if happiness is something that we have to go out --</span>
